'''Garoo''' were [[Shaman/Legends|shamans]] of the [[Dantari]] people of [[Dantooine/Legends|Dantooine]]. Their knowledge was preserved and transferred to their successors by oral repetition. Some of the more knowledgeable Garoo retained information about the original [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Jedi Enclave|outpost]] on Dantooine. [[Maga]] was a Garoo encountered by [[Mammon Hoole]] and [[Zak Arranda/Legends|Zak]] and [[Tash Arranda/Legends|Tash Arranda]].

